---
description: proto subsystem
globs: proto/**
alwaysApply: false
---
- When working under proto, read proto/CLAUDE.md for local detail.
- `.proto` files are the backend RPC contract: editing one regenerates the Rust service traits, Python `_backend_generated.py`, and TypeScript `@generated/backend` bindings.
- This needs a full `just check`, not just `cargo check` — stale codegen leaves service/method indices out of sync across layers and calls the wrong method.
